{{Flavour|Translocates a targeted enemy a short distance towards the caster. It cannot be resisted by willpower.}}

'''Blink Other Close''' is a monster-only spell which forces the target to [[blink]], ignoring the victim's [[willpower]]. Unlike the similarly named spell [[Blink Other]], this blink always moves the target closer to the caster, placing the target within range of the caster's powerful attack spells.

[[Formicid]]s and creatures in [[Tree Form]] cannot blink and are immune to this spell.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.12]], Blink Other Close could be negated if the spell failed to beat the target's magic resistance.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
